,"introductionText":18,"__component":82},1954,false,"Deze controle omvat:\n•\tIdentity & Access Management\n•\tNetwork Security\n\nOnze experts identificeren kwetsbaarheden en bieden praktische aanbevelingen om je digitale omgeving te versterken. Je krijgt van ons niet alleen inzicht in waar je staat, maar ook concrete stappen om je beveiliging te verbeteren met diverse tools en frameworks, zoals Microsoft Defender, Sentinel en Entra ID. \n\nSpeciale Black Friday Deal: gratis bij aanmelding in december!\nInteresse? Neem [contact](https://www.sharevalue.nl/contact) met ons op!\n\nP.s. heb je behoefte aan een meer uitgebreide controle? Uiteraard is dat mogelijk. Wij kunnen onderdelen controleren zoals Endpoint Security, Application Security, Data Security, Threat Detection & Response en Governance en Risk & Compliance. We lichten deze mogelijkheden graag aan je toe.\n","global.pagesection",{"id":84,"titleLeft":85,"callToActionTextLeft":86,"callToActionLinkUrlLeft":87,"titleRight":88,"callToActionTextRight":89,"callToActionLinkUrlRight":90,"iconUrlLeft":91,"iconUrlRight":104,"__component":116},247,"Heb je een Microsoft of Azure expert nodig?","Neem contact met ons op","/contact","Heb je onze klantcases al gelezen?","Klik hier voor een overzicht","/kennisbank/klantcases",{"id":92,"name":93,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":94,"height":95,"formats":18,"hash":96,"ext":97,"mime":98,"size":99,"url":100,"previewUrl":18,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":101,"updatedAt":102,"documentId":103,"publishedAt":58,"focalPoint":18},6,"bulb.svg",71,70,"bulb_dd2e1d4efb",".svg","image/svg+xml",3.75,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/bulb_dd2e1d4efb.svg","2023-08-17T08:31:37.036Z","2025-04-01T14:08:08.648Z","l2lglwkh4lf7ip36sjvs42rc",{"id":105,"name":106,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":107,"height":107,"formats":18,"hash":108,"ext":109,"mime":110,"size":111,"url":112,"previewUrl":18,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":113,